content: I'm disappointed that by now we only can use half the futures of the site. I was hoping users would be able to use an even better team builder. I think the app is extremely bare-bones and white unnecessary as it is.
Please make the app smoother. Even on high end phones this app lags a lot
Hoping for a team builder or a Save option like the website, but otherwise excellent app.
Great resource for information. Hoping for more functionality like a teambuilder, and a damage calc option.
Can you guys update the tiers like uu, bss, bsd. Also a team builder would be a nice touch since most times im not at a computer for team ideas
Thank you for bringing the app to Android but it would have been great if it wasn't just a port of the iOS app. Maybe android design language should be used in a future version.
The best resource online to see how the metas are shaping up and planning what you need to consider when making a team.
It has all the latest info you need to build your OP team and get to the top! Or at least try to. But hey! knowing is half the battle ;)
